we've watched the movie?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"Ah, about that. The movie that Arisa-chan wanted to see doesn't actually start until 1:15, so we still have a bit of time.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"But if we don't get there early we won't be able to sit in the good seats. Wouldn't it be best if we started heading there now?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"I went ahead and reserved four spots online yesterday. We should be okay either way.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Wow~! Nice going, Rimi-rin~!\nYou're the best~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"No, no. I was just looking forward to spending the day with you all.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"So, we still have time to spare...\nWhat should we do, then?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"I vote karaoke!\nWho's with me?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"Vetoed!\nKaraoke is last, got it?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"angry02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Aw, too bad...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"Besides, aren't we suppose to be taking care of our summer to-do lists? Everybody did think about what they wanted to do today, right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"Uhm, well... What I wanted was for the five of us to enjoy some chocolate sweets at the food court...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"Chocolate sweets?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"During summer break, there was a three-day chocolate fair held at the department store. I wanted to go together, but it was just bad timing...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"I see, that's definitely something worthy of putting on the list.\nHow about you, Saya?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"I... don't really have anything that I want to do. Oh, but I did actually think about it. I promise. Nothing came to mind, is all.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"What's the best way of putting it...? Spending another day together is all I need. Really.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Aw, we came all the way here, Saya~. You've gotta pick something to do with us~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"Fufu, alright.\nI'll give it a bit more thought.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"That just leaves O-Tae, right? \nHey, O-Tae... Huh?\nWhere'd she run off to?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"There she is! Over there! She's checking out something over at the knick-knack shop.\nLet's go see, too!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"... Living in her own world as usual.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"O-Tae~♪ What'cha lookin' at?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"This. Isn't it just adorable?\nA rabbit-shaped bento box.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"It is kind of cute, I'll admit. But I think this bunny addiction of yours has a little too much control over your life.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Here's a chopstick container to go with it! It has a delightful little picture of two rabbits lined up side-by-side~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"That one is brown, so it might be a hare. Hares change their fur to brown or gray in the summer.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Animals with fur can change color?! I thought that was only for chameleons!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"Well, actually...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"Hey, Saya-chan, have you looked over here yet? They have so many hair accessories!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"Show me, show me! Wow, has this store always had these?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"This hair clip totally suits you! Here, the one with the yellow marble pattern!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"Oh no... I'm a total sucker for ones like this. Agh, now I seriously wanna buy it~. I'll be in a pinch if I blow my allowance so early in the month, though...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"Ah, I see...\nThat makes things a bit difficult...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"If I don't buy it now, though, they may be sold out later.\nWhat should I do...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"O-Tae, check this out!\nI think you'll really like this phone case.\nIt's got bunny ears on it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"I'll take it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"At least think about it!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"This store does have a nice collection of phone cases~. I like this folio one. Don't you have one like this, Kasumi? How is it?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Yeah, I totally recommend that kind of case! They keep your screen from getting smudges, and you can keep your train pass in the side sleeve!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"And they seem simple and mature. Maybe I'll get one, too. Do you think I could pull this one off, Arisa-chan?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"Sure, why not? But maybe go with a lighter shade of pink, instead.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Rimi-rin, this one will be perfect, then! It is lighter and has a nice design, don't ya think?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-052","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"Hm... Now I'm confused...\nI don't know which one to get~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"awate01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"evenr53-02-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"Nah, I understand. Having so many choices just makes it harder to choose, right~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{